</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl pb-[50px]">Giving helpful feedback</h1>
	  <p class="mb-5">
        Learn a simple approach to giving feedback that is clear, respectful, and useful in everyday work situations.
      </p>

	  <div class="p-6">
  <div class="text-white badge badge-neutral badge-outline">2 hours</div>
</div>



      <!--<button class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</button> -->
